<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Password Reset - AuthKit</title>
    <style>
        body {
            font-family: 'Segoe UI', Tahoma, Geneva, Verdana, sans-serif;
            background-color: #f9f9f9;
            margin: 0;
            padding: 0;
            color: #333333;
        }
        .container {
            max-width: 600px;
            margin: 40px auto;
            background-color: #ffffff;
            padding: 30px;
            border-radius: 8px;
            box-shadow: 0 0 15px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1);
        }
        .header {
            text-align: center;
            margin-bottom: 25px;
        }
        .header img {
            max-width: 120px;
            margin-bottom: 15px;
        }
        h2 {
            color: #1a1a1a;
            font-size: 24px;
            margin-bottom: 15px;
        }
        p {
            color: #555555;
            font-size: 16px;
            line-height: 1.7;
            margin: 0 0 15px;
        }
        .btn-link {
            display: inline-block;
            background-color: #007BFF;
            color: #ffffff;
            padding: 12px 24px;
            text-decoration: none;
            border-radius: 5px;
            font-size: 16px;
            font-weight: bold;
            margin: 25px 0;
            transition: background-color 0.3s ease;
        }
        .btn-link:hover {
            background-color: #0056b3;
        }
        .footer {
            font-size: 14px;
            color: #777777;
            margin-top: 30px;
            text-align: center;
        }
        .footer a {
            color: #007BFF;
            text-decoration: none;
        }
        .footer a:hover {
            text-decoration: underline;
        }
        span{
            color: white;
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>
    <div class="container">
        <div class="header">
            <img src="https://res.cloudinary.com/dil9kylo3/image/upload/v1723176952/erlgxgiyvgbfxmizkbfa.png" alt="AuthKit Logo">
            <h2>Password Reset Request</h2>
        </div>

        <p>Dear {{name}},</p>

        <p>
            We received a request to reset the password associated with your AuthKit account. If you initiated this request, please click the button below to proceed. This link will remain active for 1 hour.
        </p> 

        <a href="{{link}}" class="btn-link"><span>Reset Your Password</span></a>
        
        <p>If you did not request a password reset, please disregard this email. Your account will remain secure, and no changes will be made.</p>

        <p>If you require further assistance, feel free to contact our support team.</p>

        <div class="footer">
            <p>
                If the "Reset Your Password" button above does not work, please copy and paste the following link into your web browser:
                <br/>
                <a href="{{link}}">{{link}}</a>
            </p>
            <p>Thank you for using AuthKit. We value your trust.</p>
        </div>
    </div>
</body>
</html>
